OL,6,FSir Andy, who has been chief inspector
OL,7,Fsince 2022 and was previously chief
OL,8,Fconstable of Merseyside Police, said:
OL,9,F"I'm a firm believer that non-crime
OL,10,Fhate incidents are no longer required,
OL,11,Fand that intelligence can be gathered
OL,12,Fin a different way, which would cause
OL,13,Fless concern to the public and would
OL,14,Fmake recording of such issues much
OL,15,Feasier for policing.
