OL,11,Fthe arrest of Father Ted writer Graham
OL,12,FLinehan, who was stopped by officers
OL,13,Fat Heathrow Airport and questioned
OL,14,Fover X entries he had made about trans
OL,15,Fissues.
OL,17,FAsked about the arrest, Sir Andy said:
OL,18,F"Was it a great public optic? No, it
OL,19,Fwasn't. Is there individual criticism
OL,20,Ffrom me in relation to the officers
OL,21,Fwho were there? No, there isn't.
